text: Gymboree is a sub brand of The Children's Place. It began with operating retail stores between the early 1970s and the later 2010s. It was founded by Joan Barnes. On January 17, 2019, the company filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy protection, and eliminated all Gymboree, Gymboree Outlet, and Crazy 8 brick- and-mortar formats as a result.
